---
title: Cheesy Panko Crumbed Chicken with Mashed Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: Can you get a more perfectly portioned plate? This balanced meal has a healthy serve of chicken breast covered in cheesy
goodness, a crunchy herb crumb, smooth mash and aromatic garlic veggies. Delish!

